title: Can you suggest some good alternative rock songs? - Quora

response.answer_text: Alternative Rock is an all encompassing genre.For example, Tame Impala - Elephant (Neo-Psychedelia)  The Strokes - Reptilia (Garage Rock)  Mew - Satellites (Space Rock)  Grimes - Oblivion (Alt Pop)  Anamaguchi - Endless Fantasy (Chiptune)  Slowdive - Crazy for You (Shoegaze)  The Stone Roses - I Wanna be Adored (Madchester)  The Mars Volta - Inertiatic ESP (Prog Rock)  Brand New - Sic Transit Gloria...Glory Fades (Emo)  All of these are considered Alternative Rock to various degrees. So have your pick.

you could try various songs from the collections of LINKIN PARK and GREEN DAY Numb (Official Video) - Linkin Park In The End (Official Video) - Linkin Park New Divide (Official Video) - Linkin Park Castle of Glass (Official Video) - Linkin Park Burn It Down (Official Video) - Linkin Park Faint (Official Video) - Linkin Park Green Day: "Boulevard Of Broken Dreams" - [Official Video] Green Day - 21 Guns [Official Music Video] Green Day - American Idiot [OFFICIAL VIDEO] Green Day - Wake Me Up When September Ends [Official Music Video] Green Day: "Holiday" - [Official Video]
